Title: Full Speed
Writer: Frédéric Jardin (scenario), Fabrice Roger-Lacan (scenario), Fabrice Roger-Lacan (adaptation), Nicolas Benamou (adaptation)
Actors: José Garcia, André Dussollier, Caroline Vigneaux, Charlotte Gabris
Plot: A family together with their grandpa go on a vacation, when their new car won't stop and it nearly escapes crashing into a hundred cars.
